Day 49
--------------
Step 1) Test case: Account Registration

Setting up the project
Adding dependencies, creating folder structure, packages, classes, test cases etc..
Writing test cases for Account Registration

--------------
Day 50
--------------
Step 2) Adding logs to test case (log4j2)

Logging - record all the events in the form of text
Log Levels - All < Trace < Debug < Info < Warn < Error < Fatal < Off
Appenders - where you want to generate the log (console/file)
Loggers - what type of log you want to generate (All < Trace < Debug < Info < Warn < Error < Fatal < Off)
Dependencies - log4j-core, log4j-api